===Etymology===
:from the Late Latin ''verbalis'', belonging to a word.

===[[Adjective]]===
#spoken, as opposed to written.
#[grammar]: derived from a verb, as a verbal noun or verbal adjective.

===[[Noun]]===
#[grammar]: a verb form which does not function as a [[predicate]], or a word derived from a verb. In English, [[infinitive]]s, [[participle]]s and [[gerund]]s are verbals.